<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2018/02/12/spring-session-1-3-2-released">Spring Session 1.3.2 Released</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon releases"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/releases">Releases</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="https://gravatar.com/avatar/30ed046efb35c67d4c055dab109b8933?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<a class="author" href="/team/rwinch">Rob Winch</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2018-02-12 15:58:30.057">February 12, 2018</time>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="3165" href="/blog/2018/02/12/spring-session-1-3-2-released#disqus_thread">
</a></div>
</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><div class="paragraph">
<p><em>This post was authored by <a href="https://github.com/vpavic">Vedran Pavić</a></em></p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>On behalf of the community I’m pleased to announce the release of <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-session/docs/1.3.2.RELEASE/reference/html5/">Spring Session 1.3.2.RELEASE</a>. This maintenance release contains numerous bug fixes and improvements.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Some of the highlights include:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li> <p><a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-session/issues/951">#951</a> - <code>SessionRepositoryFilter#changeSessionId</code> does not copy the previous <code>maxInactiveInterval</code> into the new session</p> </li>
<li> <p><a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-session/issues/983">#983</a> - Optimize <code>HazelcastSessionRepository</code> write operations</p> </li>
<li> <p><a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-session/issues/984">#984</a> - Improve session event handling</p> </li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can find the complete details of the release in the <a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-session/milestone/33?closed=1">changelog</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
